com.google.template.soy.basetree

Class SyntaxVersionBound

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.template.soy.basetree.SyntaxVersionBound

  • public final class SyntaxVersionBound
extends Object
    Value class representing a known upper bound for the syntax version of a node.

    Important: Do not use outside of Soy code (treat as superpackage-private).
